text: Nabiyow isi Rabbi kallacak Yi- Rabbow Reeda inkih lem koo Atu Reeda isih faxxa marah taceeh isih faxxa marak Reeda kaltaah Seelabtah, Atu Addunyal isih faxxa mara fayya haytaah taysiiseeh isih faxxa mara Ramma haytaah xixxibissa, Yi-Rabbow kayri inkih ku-gabat yan, Diggah Atu ummaan iimih dudda lito ixxic
